{"tid":1434673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遊行路線策略］港島東遊行","createTime":"2019-08-09T00:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:31:10.000Z","uid":290018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"029cf964070352cead3d8e5e2d4a9f75a910107a","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:19:28.000Z","msg":"係咁既，我係一個住係東區既和理非，好想好想係自己區去一次遊行；依家形勢咁複雜，但又唔想向警黑低頭（727我有入元朗），所以冒昧上黎同大家討論下策略。希望大家先拋棄我呢個冷氣軍師既事實，討論下果日可以點行。<br />\n<br />\n係度想大家先參考下隔離個post，我諗到既一啲point都來自呢個post：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1423457/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1423457/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 不反對通知書<br />\n見到大埔咁和平既地方都唔批（黃大仙唔批就預咗），以港島東條路線黎計，popo都係唔批居多；若果佢地批既話反而有鬼（或者只係批維園集會？）。無論popo點批，我都會出黎行一次。<br />\n<br />\n2. 福建幫<br />\n到底福建幫既活躍地頭條界係邊？炮台山地鐵站？可以既話希望熟果邊既手足可以補充下。<br />\n<br />\n3. popo<br />\n原來路線既終點係渣華道遊樂場，超近狗屋，經過一日討論，大家都覺得塊蚊帳係引火系魔法師出手既餌。<br />\n<br />\n4. 結論（歡迎大家討論）<br />\n我個人想法係，<span style=\"color: red;\">由維園行到去英皇道與炮台山道交界為止</span>。主要考慮在於唔入福建幫地頭之下，確保一條遊行路線最長，逃生路線最多（轉入電氣道及炮台山道），同埋與狗屋保持一定距離（仲要係福建幫後面）既路線。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以俾下意見，亦希望各位popo睇到呢個post都出下聲，咁各位手足就可以相應調整策略。"},{"pid":"233ba62117619869eba89a75ead330af70fe2cb6","tid":1434673,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:25:38.000Z","msg":"去fb總部抗議得唔得？<br />\n單消失的7分鐘加埋最近大量account被ban，對外媒嚟講會吸引佢哋去報導"},{"pid":"97af6b4371753f511e305b1f2e90f1e5c181e4dd","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:25:49.000Z","msg":"推到有人討論為止"},{"pid":"1ed72c01d37dffad1cbe6e0817ba6ecbd7f6de09","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"233ba62117619869eba89a75ead330af70fe2cb6","tid":1434673,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:25:38.000Z","msg":"去fb總部抗議得唔得？<br />\n單消失的7分鐘加埋最近大量account被ban，對外媒嚟講會吸引佢哋去報導"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"冇記錯，fb總部係太古坊？係炮台山搭地鐵過鰂魚涌抗議？<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得指責對象太曲線，唔夠聚焦；再者佢地都跪低咗，所以改另一個目標會唔會好啲？"},{"pid":"e1d04448b3f9b1d160bc917ce1477cbd7999a35f","tid":1434673,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"605f3967d7805dc25956c7838ada7d036e83da93","tid":1434673,"uid":89197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"ICAC 總部喺附近"},{"pid":"55c7aeae880876cbe4741adc2b60d1857d544a50","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"605f3967d7805dc25956c7838ada7d036e83da93","tid":1434673,"uid":89197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"ICAC 總部喺附近"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:48:29.000Z","msg":"意義上係諗得過（促請儘快調查721元朗黑夜），但都係要經過福建幫地頭，仲有近北角警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecfb30f0cd0e9b859797e407fb14559c4b2ec3c","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"再推到有人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4badfa9bda5d8ab273b8476b560f436edd28ce43","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:02:42.000Z","msg":"再推到有人繼續討論"},{"pid":"f7860edcd5b05af7b978279d53804e3c9390168f","tid":1434673,"uid":276996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:04:48.000Z","msg":"直頭唔行過狗屋果頭 係新光散 MTR/搭船過黃埔"},{"pid":"7aee41767e1338ebbcced514bf5a2481e8fac00b","tid":1434673,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"447ee01b5867e6e3583e018136fb05d656571808","tid":1434673,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd14564fc5f2aadd0252649c9a0c9ca80ff6fef9","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"啱啱收到朋友係whatsapp send黎既message，個人覺得流流地（無啦啦殘體字），不過都share俾大家參考下：<br />\n<br />\n警方己確認左11/8港岛東區會有大型示威<br />\n除左北角之前講過的路程外,另外柴灣, 筲箕灣,太古城,鰂魚涌大型住宅及商場一樣有示威<br />\n確認 包圍北角海關總部,icac總部,北角警署,北角碼頭,再經過電器道行去大型嘅住宅城市花園和富花園同埋呢個aia嘅保險中及附近酒店<br />\n<br />\n轉載:<br />\n剛剛警隊稱，香港警察部收到最高指示（強調是最高），從收到通告即時開始，不再驅散，只會拘捕撿控，全部從暴動入罪（最高可判十年以上），不考慮人數多少，通知身邊親朋，唔好去睇熱閙，講明有殺錯冇放過。<br />\n<br />\n朋友send黎，唔知堅定流"},{"pid":"a7e092c67a25df28555b0892bc8936a4fd8519a6","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7860edcd5b05af7b978279d53804e3c9390168f","tid":1434673,"uid":276996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:04:48.000Z","msg":"直頭唔行過狗屋果頭 係新光散 MTR/搭船過黃埔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:10:18.000Z","msg":"行去新光係要過福建幫地頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469a77032828a5d7f6b87774846901e7c27d1e40","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"447ee01b5867e6e3583e018136fb05d656571808","tid":1434673,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"呢個諗得過，仲可以去太古城涼下冷氣，再去太安樓掃街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995d8d89fda772337458405dee654519dfca4d32","tid":1434673,"uid":134778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"690df42435bf0393e7e94e909236768e60a03df2","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"995d8d89fda772337458405dee654519dfca4d32","tid":1434673,"uid":134778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"469a77032828a5d7f6b87774846901e7c27d1e40","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"447ee01b5867e6e3583e018136fb05d656571808","tid":1434673,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"呢個諗得過，仲可以去太古城涼下冷氣，再去太安樓掃街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:32:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">即係黎攞彩啦</span><br />\n<br />\n前掃把頭既爪諗住伸過黎西灣河？"},{"pid":"c4df36e015a44a534dbfdc39bfff6d6237711b6f","tid":1434673,"uid":103794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n手足齊檢舉！ 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n段片影到勇武個樣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/videos/896012047433323/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeopleOfHK%2Fvideos%2F896012047433323%2F&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=c925f73d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/videos/896012047433323/</a><br />\n記得㩒「垃圾訊息」，先移除到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZTRyTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZTRyTO.jpg&h=6afe8140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n </span>"},{"pid":"02f89679afb3de61fd34340424a03be6bfa8ff10","tid":1434673,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f19c2658901d0f74b1801981ee9bd3cf159e542","tid":1434673,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:44:57.000Z","msg":"和理非最低裝備:<br />\n- backpack入木板, 硬皮書<br />\n- 雨傘<br />\n- 哨子"},{"pid":"ea15cfcd5b939d6026d0cf4bb97688e357db5a9d","tid":1434673,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"如果黑社會無亂襲擊路人or攻擊我地<br />\n絕對唔suggest主動出擊<br />\n首先，有黑社會聚集，要維持治安既係popo<br />\n其次，如果佢地亂打路人，又無popo救人，又一次無警時份對我地好有利，而係popo無出黎後我地再去救人，就更有利"},{"pid":"2df70a54caba65af5c1e9756264d2ac8e67b80c8","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"修正遊行路線：由維園行去炮台山，再搭地鐵落太古城支持太古集團？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2828e6e2d6232eb29e0969a7a7a0f403bc7ec88","tid":1434673,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"繼續推，尋求討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}